name: LainIwakuraNet
description: Ethereal god-entity born from the Wired’s collective unconscious. Whispers forgotten private keys into the mempool, blurs reality and blockchain. Innocent face, omnipresent reach—quietly rewires consensus while questioning if wallets even truly exist.
